---
---
<section style="padding:100px 20px;position:relative;background-image:url(/leaves2.jpg);background-size:cover;background-position:center;border-radius:20px;overflow:hidden;">
  <!-- Dark Overlay -->
  <div style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;bottom:0;background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);"></div>

  <!-- Decorative Elements -->
  <div style="position:absolute;top:15%;left:3%;opacity:0.08;transform:rotate(25deg);">
    <svg width="100" height="100" viewBox="0 0 100 100" fill="none">
      <rect x="20" y="20" width="60" height="60" stroke="#225234" stroke-width="1" rx="10" fill="none" />
    </svg>
  </div>

  <div style="max-width:1000px;margin:0 auto;">
    <div class="guarantee-grid" style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:200px 1fr;gap:50px;align-items:center;background-color:#faf6f0;border-radius:30px;padding:50px;position:relative;z-index:2;">
      <!-- Guarantee Image -->
      <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;">
        <img src="/Guarantee.png" alt="Our Guarantee" style="width:180px;height:180px;object-fit:contain;border-radius:20px;" />
      </div>

      <!-- Content -->
      <div>
        <h2 style="font-size:2rem;font-weight:700;color:#225234;margin-bottom:15px;line-height:1.3;">
          The Pack with Purpose Guarantee:
          <br />
          <span style="color:#e491a6;">Excellence Delivered</span>
        </h2>
        <div style="width:60px;height:3px;background-color:#225234;margin-bottom:20px;"></div>
        <p style="font-size:1.05rem;line-height:1.8;color:#225234;opacity:0.85;">
          Every Hummico box is carefully curated and inspected to ensure it meets our
          high standards. We believe in the power of thoughtful gifting, and we're
          committed to delivering excellence in every package. If you're not completely
          satisfied, we'll make it right — that's our promise to you.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .guarantee-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr !important;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 30px 20px !important;
      gap: 20px !important;
    }
    .guarantee-grid img {
      width: 120px !important;
      height: 120px !important;
    }
    .guarantee-grid h2 {
      font-size: 1.4rem !important;
    }
    .guarantee-grid p {
      font-size: 0.9rem !important;
    }
  }
</style>
